high_descs: Move to the right to the counter to the left of the sink.
Take the knife from the counter.
Move to the right and face forward the sink.
Cut the potato in the middle of the potato and the egg into slices.
Put the knife in the sink.
Take a slice of potato from the sink.
Turn right, go forward, turn left to face the fridge.
Put the potato on the upper shelf of the bottom fridge compartment. Close then open the fridge. Take the potato from the fridge.
Turn left, go forward to the white table, turn right to face the black stand.
Put the slice of potato to the right of the potato on the stand.
anns.task_desc: Put a slice of cold potato on a stand.

high_descs: Walk a few steps to the right to get closer to the sink.
Pick up the yellow knife from the counter top.
Walk to your right to get to the front of the sink.
Cut the potato in the middle of an egg and a potato.
Put the knife on top of the whole potato.
Pick up a slice of the potato.
Walk to the right and turn to the black fridge.
Open the fridge, put the slice of potato on the rack, close the fridge, let it cool for a few seconds, open the fridge, pick up the potato and close the fridge.
Turn left, walk to the end of the room and turn right to go to the black shelf.
Put the slice of potato on the black shelf.
anns.task_desc: Put a cold slice of potato on the black shelf at the corner of the room.

high_descs: Move over to your right so that you are directly in front of the kitchen counter to the left of the sink.
Pick up the knife on the counter, all the way in the back.
Move over to your right again so that you are directly in front of the kitchen sink.
Cut the potato in the sink that is between another potato and an egg.
Place the knife in the sink next to the potato that was just sliced.
Pick up one of the potato slices in the sink.
Turn to your right and walk over to the refrigerator.
Place the potato in the refrigerator on the top shelf, wait a moment for the potato to chill then remove the potato from the refrigerator.
Turn to your left and walk over to the small, black shelf between the kitchen counter and the black, garbage bag on the floor.
Place the potato slice on the small, black shelf, between the whole potato and the kitchen counter.
anns.task_desc: Put a chilled potato slice on the small, black shelf.

high_descs: Turn slightly to the right and face the counter
Grab the knife that's on the counter
Turn right and stop at the counter
Cut the potato in the sink into slices
Place the knife in the sink
Grab a slice of the potato
Turn right and stop at the fridge
Open the bottom door of the fridge and put the potato on the top rack. Close the door. Open the door and take the potato out.
Turn left and head to the black table
Place the potato on the table
anns.task_desc: Putting a potato slice on the black table

high_descs: Move a few inches to the right.
Pick the knife up off the counter.
Move a few steps to the sink on your right.
Slice the potato in the middle of the other two potatoes.
Put the knife in the sink on top of the front potato.
Pick up a slice of potato.
Move to the fridge on your right.
Cool the potato slice on the top shelf of the fridge for a few seconds and then take it back out.
Turn left and move across the room to the black rack on your right.
Put the potato slice on the rack next to the potato.
anns.task_desc: Put a cooled piece of potato on the top shelf of the black rack.
